Class DataRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xtech.leakvm.sdk.net.server.DataRequest

  • public class DataRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    DataRequest class is the implementation of HTTP Request, this contains Client Headers, GET, POST and Boundary Data.
